WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
الحمد بالله رب العالمين

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:07.000
الرحمن الرحيم

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:10.000
مالك يوم الدين

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:14.000
إياك نعبد وإياك نستعيم

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:17.000
اهدن الصراة المستقيم

00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:21.000
صراة الذين أنعنت عليهم

00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:24.000
غير المغضوب عليهم

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:35.230
السلام عليكم ورحمة الله وبركاته

00:00:35.230 --> 00:00:37.230
بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم

00:00:37.230 --> 00:00:39.230
الحمد لله رب العالمين

00:00:39.230 --> 00:00:41.230
وبه نستعين ونصلي ونسلم

00:00:41.230 --> 00:00:43.230
على أفضل الخلق أجمعين

00:00:43.230 --> 00:00:45.230
نبينا محمد وعلى آله وصحبه

00:00:45.230 --> 00:00:47.230
والتابعين ومن تبعهم

00:00:47.230 --> 00:00:49.230
بإحسان إلى يوم الدين وبعه

00:00:49.230 --> 00:00:52.230
We commence by praising Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:00:52.230 --> 00:00:54.230
sending blessings and salutations

00:00:54.230 --> 00:00:56.230
upon Muhammad صلى الله عليه وسلم

00:00:56.230 --> 00:00:58.230
and his entire household

00:00:58.230 --> 00:01:00.230
may Allah bless them all, his companions as well

00:01:00.230 --> 00:01:02.230
and may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:01:02.230 --> 00:01:04.230
bless every single one of us

00:01:04.230 --> 00:01:06.230
all goodness

00:01:06.230 --> 00:01:10.230
beloved brothers and sisters in Islam

00:01:10.230 --> 00:01:12.230
we were in the midst of the battle of

00:01:12.230 --> 00:01:14.230
the ahzab, the battle of the confederates

00:01:14.230 --> 00:01:16.230
and we had made mention of how

00:01:16.230 --> 00:01:18.230
Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:01:18.230 --> 00:01:20.230
sent a powerful wind

00:01:20.230 --> 00:01:22.230
and some rain, tornado

00:01:22.230 --> 00:01:24.230
and Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:01:24.230 --> 00:01:26.230
dispersed them

00:01:26.230 --> 00:01:28.230
it is important that we make mention

00:01:28.230 --> 00:01:31.230
of the time of digging the trench

00:01:31.230 --> 00:01:33.230
when they were digging the trench

00:01:33.230 --> 00:01:36.230
as we had said, a 10 kilometer long trench

00:01:36.230 --> 00:01:41.230
22 feet wide, 16 feet deep

00:01:41.230 --> 00:01:44.230
subhanAllah, it was a large trench

00:01:44.230 --> 00:01:46.230
mashaAllah, and it was only

00:01:46.230 --> 00:01:49.230
around parts of Medina Munawwara

00:01:49.230 --> 00:01:51.230
and we made mention of the reason of that

00:01:51.230 --> 00:01:54.960
the Prophet صلى الله عليه وسلم

00:01:54.960 --> 00:01:57.960
and his companions were so dedicated in digging

00:01:57.960 --> 00:01:59.960
that they would not leave

00:01:59.960 --> 00:02:01.960
even to relieve themselves

00:02:01.960 --> 00:02:03.960
without the permission of Rasulullah صلى الله عليه وسلم

00:02:04.960 --> 00:02:06.960
whenever they needed to do something

00:02:06.960 --> 00:02:08.960
they would ask his permission and then leave

00:02:08.960 --> 00:02:11.960
it was easy for them to go and to come back

00:02:11.960 --> 00:02:13.960
without really being noticed, but

00:02:13.960 --> 00:02:16.960
they were so honest, they did not want to be seen

00:02:16.960 --> 00:02:20.960
as people who were not fulfilling their duty

00:02:20.960 --> 00:02:23.960
or making others do what they are supposed to be doing

00:02:23.960 --> 00:02:25.960
you see when it comes to hard work

00:02:25.960 --> 00:02:27.960
many people have a bad habit, that is

00:02:27.960 --> 00:02:29.960
they wait for others to do the hard work

00:02:29.960 --> 00:02:31.960
and then the name is theirs, mashaAllah

00:02:31.960 --> 00:02:33.960
you know the work is someone else's

00:02:33.960 --> 00:02:35.960
and they want to join in whenever there is goodness

00:02:35.960 --> 00:02:38.960
and they say we achieved, but where were you my brother?

00:02:38.960 --> 00:02:39.960
you were nowhere to be seen

00:02:39.960 --> 00:02:42.960
so the sahabah were not like that

00:02:42.960 --> 00:02:45.960
they used to work very hard and they were from amongst those

00:02:45.960 --> 00:02:47.960
ask the Prophet صلى الله عليه وسلم

00:02:47.960 --> 00:02:48.960
I need to go, I will come back

00:02:48.960 --> 00:02:52.960
and Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala praises them in the Quran

00:02:52.960 --> 00:02:54.960
using the following words

00:02:54.960 --> 00:03:21.660
...

00:03:21.660 --> 00:03:24.660
the true believers are those who believe in Allah

00:03:24.660 --> 00:03:26.660
and in the messenger

00:03:26.660 --> 00:03:29.660
and when they are engaged in some collective activity

00:03:29.660 --> 00:03:34.660
they do not leave except after seeking permission

00:03:34.660 --> 00:03:36.660
and Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala says

00:03:36.660 --> 00:03:38.660
those who seek your permission

00:03:38.660 --> 00:03:41.660
they are true believers in Allah and His messenger

00:03:41.660 --> 00:03:42.660
صلى الله عليه وسلم

00:03:42.660 --> 00:03:44.660
and Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala says

00:03:44.660 --> 00:03:46.660
from amongst those who seek your permission

00:03:46.660 --> 00:03:48.660
you may permit them

00:03:48.660 --> 00:03:49.660
he used to permit them

00:03:49.660 --> 00:03:52.660
but he had the option of not allowing them as well

00:03:52.660 --> 00:03:55.660
yet he used to allow them صلى الله عليه وسلم

00:03:55.660 --> 00:04:01.660
another very important statement made by Rasulullah صلى الله عليه وسلم

00:04:01.660 --> 00:04:04.660
during that time when they were digging

00:04:04.660 --> 00:04:08.660
and the dua that was being made when the enemies had come

00:04:08.660 --> 00:04:09.660
he used to say

00:04:19.660 --> 00:04:20.660
the meaning of which is

00:04:20.660 --> 00:04:24.660
there is none worthy of worship besides Allah alone

00:04:24.660 --> 00:04:27.660
he has fulfilled his promise to his worshipper

00:04:27.660 --> 00:04:30.660
Allah promised him victory

00:04:30.660 --> 00:04:32.660
and he has assisted his slave

00:04:34.660 --> 00:04:38.660
and he has granted strength to his army

00:04:38.660 --> 00:04:41.660
strength was granted to the Muslim army

00:04:41.660 --> 00:04:47.660
and he has destroyed the confederates on his own

00:04:47.660 --> 00:04:49.660
which means it was Allah

00:04:49.660 --> 00:04:52.660
who chased away these allies

00:04:52.660 --> 00:04:55.660
and it was Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala's help

00:04:55.660 --> 00:04:57.660
he is the one who sent the wind

00:04:57.660 --> 00:04:59.660
and the angels as Allah says

00:05:10.660 --> 00:05:15.660
remember the time when the forces came against you

00:05:15.660 --> 00:05:18.660
and we sent upon them the wind

00:05:18.660 --> 00:05:21.660
and armies that you could not see from amongst the angels

00:05:21.660 --> 00:05:25.660
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala protect us always

00:05:25.660 --> 00:05:29.660
also we should know a lesson for all of us

00:05:29.660 --> 00:05:34.660
the help of Allah comes after great test and difficulty

00:05:34.660 --> 00:05:37.660
when you are in the hardest moments of your life

00:05:37.660 --> 00:05:39.660
you should know the doors are about to open

00:05:39.660 --> 00:05:42.660
you are the closest to the opening of the doors

00:05:42.660 --> 00:05:44.660
and this is something which is sunnatullah

00:05:44.660 --> 00:05:46.660
it is the plan of Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:05:46.660 --> 00:05:47.660
the system of Allah

00:05:47.660 --> 00:05:49.660
the Quran is full of verses that show us

00:05:49.660 --> 00:05:53.660
that Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala has tested prophet after prophet

00:05:53.660 --> 00:05:57.660
until when they were at the peak of the test

00:05:57.660 --> 00:05:59.660
the doors opened one after the other

00:05:59.660 --> 00:06:01.660
and Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala granted them help

00:06:01.660 --> 00:06:04.660
so this is a point of comfort for us all

00:06:04.660 --> 00:06:07.660
in life when we are going through difficulties

00:06:07.660 --> 00:06:08.660
do not despair

00:06:08.660 --> 00:06:10.660
sometimes you get to the peak and you think

00:06:10.660 --> 00:06:12.660
you know what there is nothing I can do now

00:06:12.660 --> 00:06:13.660
I am fed up I am tired

00:06:13.660 --> 00:06:16.660
no it is the point to turn to Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:06:16.660 --> 00:06:18.660
never lose hope in His mercy

00:06:18.660 --> 00:06:21.660
you are the closest you ever were to the doors of victory

00:06:21.660 --> 00:06:24.660
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala protect us

00:06:24.660 --> 00:06:27.660
and grant us ease in every of our difficulties

00:06:27.660 --> 00:06:30.660
also when the prophet salallahu alayhi wasallam

00:06:30.660 --> 00:06:33.660
was destroying one of the huge boulders

00:06:33.660 --> 00:06:34.660
that the sahabah radiallahu anhu

00:06:34.660 --> 00:06:36.660
could not destroy

00:06:36.660 --> 00:06:38.660
as he said Allah akbar

00:06:38.660 --> 00:06:42.660
and took the hammer and knocked the boulder

00:06:42.660 --> 00:06:44.660
he broke it into one piece

00:06:44.660 --> 00:06:46.660
and he said Allah akbar

00:06:46.660 --> 00:06:50.660
I have just been given the keys to Asham

00:06:50.660 --> 00:06:54.660
which means Allah has granted me victory over Asham

00:06:54.660 --> 00:06:56.660
the Syrian Palestinian region

00:06:56.660 --> 00:06:58.660
as we would call it today

00:06:58.660 --> 00:07:00.660
known as Asham at that time

00:07:00.660 --> 00:07:02.660
and subhanallah he says

00:07:02.660 --> 00:07:04.660
I can see its palaces

00:07:04.660 --> 00:07:06.660
this was when he struck it the first time

00:07:06.660 --> 00:07:07.660
he struck it again

00:07:07.660 --> 00:07:08.660
he says Allah akbar

00:07:08.660 --> 00:07:10.660
I have been granted Persia

00:07:10.660 --> 00:07:12.660
when he struck it again

00:07:12.660 --> 00:07:14.660
and when he struck it the third time

00:07:14.660 --> 00:07:15.660
he says Allah akbar

00:07:15.660 --> 00:07:17.660
I have been granted the keys of Yemen

00:07:17.660 --> 00:07:19.660
the third time he said this

00:07:19.660 --> 00:07:22.660
and the hypocrites were busy laughing

00:07:22.660 --> 00:07:24.660
they said this man

00:07:24.660 --> 00:07:26.660
he is promising us victory

00:07:26.660 --> 00:07:29.660
when we go out to relieve ourselves right now

00:07:29.660 --> 00:07:30.660
we are so frightened

00:07:30.660 --> 00:07:33.660
and he is telling us that he is going to be victorious

00:07:33.660 --> 00:07:36.660
and Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala made him victorious

00:07:36.660 --> 00:07:37.660
and we bear witness

00:07:37.660 --> 00:07:39.660
that Islam has spread far and wide

00:07:39.660 --> 00:07:40.660
yet at that time

00:07:40.660 --> 00:07:43.660
they were busy digging a little trench

00:07:43.660 --> 00:07:44.660
Allah akbar

00:07:44.660 --> 00:07:46.660
look at the sacrifice of the sahaba

00:07:46.660 --> 00:07:47.660
this is why we say

00:07:47.660 --> 00:07:49.660
may peace be upon them

00:07:49.660 --> 00:07:50.660
radhiyallahu anhum

00:07:50.660 --> 00:07:52.660
Allah be pleased upon them

00:07:52.660 --> 00:07:54.660
had it not been for their sacrifice

00:07:54.660 --> 00:07:56.660
one wonders where we would have been sitting today

00:07:56.660 --> 00:07:59.660
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala grant us

00:07:59.660 --> 00:08:01.660
the ability to be grateful

00:08:01.660 --> 00:08:03.660
and to ponder over the gift upon us

00:08:03.660 --> 00:08:06.660
and to ponder over the sacrifice of those

00:08:06.660 --> 00:08:07.660
and to ask ourselves

00:08:07.660 --> 00:08:09.660
what are we ready to sacrifice

00:08:09.660 --> 00:08:11.660
sometimes we are not ready to sacrifice

00:08:11.660 --> 00:08:13.660
our sleep for salah

00:08:13.660 --> 00:08:15.660
and sometimes we are not ready to sacrifice

00:08:15.660 --> 00:08:19.660
our desires to please Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:08:19.660 --> 00:08:22.660
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala protect us

00:08:22.660 --> 00:08:25.660
we had also made mention of Ikrimah ibn Abi Jahl

00:08:25.660 --> 00:08:28.660
who had tried to come through the trench

00:08:28.660 --> 00:08:30.660
and he was attacked

00:08:30.660 --> 00:08:31.660
Khalid ibn Al-Waleed

00:08:31.660 --> 00:08:33.660
who was on the side of the mushriks on that day

00:08:33.660 --> 00:08:35.660
had also tried

00:08:35.660 --> 00:08:38.660
and because he was one who was very intelligent

00:08:38.660 --> 00:08:39.660
on the day of Uhud

00:08:39.660 --> 00:08:41.660
the Prophet sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:08:41.660 --> 00:08:44.660
had set aside Usaid ibn Hudayr radhiyallahu anhu

00:08:44.660 --> 00:08:46.660
with 200 men telling him

00:08:46.660 --> 00:08:47.660
just watch Khalid

00:08:47.660 --> 00:08:50.660
just make sure that he does not come about

00:08:50.660 --> 00:08:52.660
to engage in something similar to

00:08:52.660 --> 00:08:54.660
that which he did in the past

00:08:54.660 --> 00:08:57.660
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala grant us all protection

00:08:57.660 --> 00:09:00.660
and as for the hypocrites

00:09:00.660 --> 00:09:02.660
on that day they were laughing

00:09:03.660 --> 00:09:05.660
and they said there is no chance

00:09:05.660 --> 00:09:08.660
that you people can actually be victorious

00:09:08.660 --> 00:09:11.660
over 10,000 powerful men

00:09:11.660 --> 00:09:13.660
who have come heavily armed

00:09:13.660 --> 00:09:15.660
from all different tribes and groups

00:09:15.660 --> 00:09:17.660
they have allied together

00:09:17.660 --> 00:09:18.660
and they have come against you

00:09:18.660 --> 00:09:20.660
and Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala says

00:09:20.660 --> 00:09:25.660
they sought to excuse themselves saying

00:09:25.660 --> 00:09:28.660
you know we have to look at our own homes

00:09:28.660 --> 00:09:31.660
there are difficulties we are facing

00:09:31.660 --> 00:09:33.660
women are not protected and so on

00:09:33.660 --> 00:09:34.660
so we need to go

00:09:34.660 --> 00:09:37.660
and Allah exposes them in suratul ahzab

00:09:37.660 --> 00:09:38.660
Allah says these are hypocrites

00:09:38.660 --> 00:09:39.660
they lied to you

00:09:50.660 --> 00:09:52.660
remember there was a group from amongst you

00:09:52.660 --> 00:09:53.660
who had said

00:09:53.660 --> 00:09:54.660
O people of Medina

00:09:54.660 --> 00:09:55.660
O people of Yathrib

00:09:55.660 --> 00:09:57.660
go back because you will not be able

00:09:57.660 --> 00:09:58.660
to face this enemy

00:10:01.660 --> 00:10:14.660
Arabic

00:10:14.660 --> 00:10:16.660
and the group from amongst them came to you

00:10:16.660 --> 00:10:20.660
excusing themselves with the excuse

00:10:20.660 --> 00:10:22.660
that our homes are exposed

00:10:22.660 --> 00:10:25.660
Allah says their homes were not exposed

00:10:25.660 --> 00:10:29.660
they only wanted to run away from the battlefield

00:10:29.660 --> 00:10:31.660
and this is why Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:10:31.660 --> 00:10:33.660
in suratul ahzab has revealed

00:10:33.660 --> 00:10:35.660
so many verses exposing these hypocrites

00:10:35.660 --> 00:10:37.660
and telling us

00:10:51.660 --> 00:10:53.660
say O Muhammad salallahu alayhi wasallam

00:10:53.660 --> 00:10:56.660
tell them you will never be able to run away

00:10:57.660 --> 00:10:59.660
if you are trying to run away from death

00:10:59.660 --> 00:11:01.660
or from being killed

00:11:01.660 --> 00:11:03.660
at the time that Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:11:03.660 --> 00:11:04.660
has written for you

00:11:04.660 --> 00:11:06.660
you won't be able to run away

00:11:06.660 --> 00:11:08.660
you know if we take a look at

00:11:08.660 --> 00:11:10.660
Khalid ibn al-waleed r.a

00:11:10.660 --> 00:11:12.660
at this moment he was

00:11:12.660 --> 00:11:14.660
from amongst the mushrik army

00:11:14.660 --> 00:11:16.660
later on he accepted Islam

00:11:16.660 --> 00:11:18.660
and when he passed away

00:11:18.660 --> 00:11:21.660
he passed away on his deathbed

00:11:21.660 --> 00:11:22.660
he was not a martyr

00:11:22.660 --> 00:11:24.660
who had martyred on the field of battle

00:11:24.660 --> 00:11:26.660
he passed away on his deathbed

00:11:26.660 --> 00:11:28.660
and he showed the people

00:11:28.660 --> 00:11:30.660
the gashes that he had had

00:11:30.660 --> 00:11:31.660
all over his body

00:11:31.660 --> 00:11:34.660
and he says I would just like

00:11:34.660 --> 00:11:36.660
this to serve as a lesson

00:11:36.660 --> 00:11:40.660
to those who are full of cowardice

00:11:40.660 --> 00:11:42.660
that as much as I have fought

00:11:42.660 --> 00:11:45.660
and everyone knew that Khalid ibn al-waleed

00:11:45.660 --> 00:11:47.660
he was even known as Saifullah

00:11:47.660 --> 00:11:50.660
he was known as the sword of Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:11:50.660 --> 00:11:53.660
he says as much as I fought

00:11:53.660 --> 00:11:55.660
Allah had not written death

00:11:55.660 --> 00:11:57.660
for me on the battlefield

00:11:57.660 --> 00:12:00.660
but wrote it on my bed at home

00:12:00.660 --> 00:12:05.660
so let the eyes of the coward

00:12:05.660 --> 00:12:07.660
not be sealed and closed

00:12:07.660 --> 00:12:11.660
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala grant us a lesson

00:12:11.660 --> 00:12:15.660
thereafter we had the head of Banu Qurayza

00:12:15.660 --> 00:12:17.660
whose name was Ka'b ibn Asad

00:12:17.660 --> 00:12:19.660
this Ka'b ibn Asad

00:12:19.660 --> 00:12:20.660
he had broken the treaty

00:12:20.660 --> 00:12:22.660
during the battle of the confederation

00:12:22.660 --> 00:12:24.660
the confederates that had come

00:12:24.660 --> 00:12:25.660
it is known as Ghazwatul Ahzab

00:12:25.660 --> 00:12:27.660
because they had allied together

00:12:27.660 --> 00:12:29.660
it is also known as Al-khandaq

00:12:29.660 --> 00:12:31.660
because of the trench that they had dug

00:12:31.660 --> 00:12:33.660
the Banu Qurayza broke their treaty

00:12:33.660 --> 00:12:34.660
we spoke about it yesterday

00:12:34.660 --> 00:12:36.660
this Ka'b ibn Asad

00:12:36.660 --> 00:12:39.660
he had tried to harm the Muslim women

00:12:39.660 --> 00:12:41.660
and he had tried to harm the Muslims

00:12:41.660 --> 00:12:43.660
the Prophet salallahu alayhi wasalam

00:12:43.660 --> 00:12:45.660
first sent as Zubayr ibn al-awwam

00:12:45.660 --> 00:12:46.660
radiallahu anhu

00:12:46.660 --> 00:12:49.660
tells him go and see what these people are doing

00:12:49.660 --> 00:12:51.940
he came back

00:12:51.940 --> 00:12:53.940
and he says O Messenger salallahu alayhi wasalam

00:12:53.940 --> 00:12:54.940
they are protecting themselves

00:12:54.940 --> 00:12:57.940
they are building their fort properly

00:12:57.940 --> 00:12:59.940
and they are trying to open up a pathway

00:12:59.940 --> 00:13:01.940
in order to come and attack us perhaps

00:13:01.940 --> 00:13:03.940
or in order to join those

00:13:03.940 --> 00:13:05.940
and in order to assist them

00:13:05.940 --> 00:13:07.940
so the Prophet salallahu alayhi wasalam

00:13:07.940 --> 00:13:08.940
to confirm this news

00:13:08.940 --> 00:13:10.940
he sent three people

00:13:10.940 --> 00:13:13.940
he sent Sa'd ibn Mu'adh, Sa'd ibn Ubadah

00:13:13.940 --> 00:13:14.940
and Abdullah ibn Rawaha

00:13:14.940 --> 00:13:16.940
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala be pleased with them

00:13:16.940 --> 00:13:18.940
with them a group of people

00:13:18.940 --> 00:13:19.940
go and check

00:13:19.940 --> 00:13:21.940
go and see what is happening

00:13:21.940 --> 00:13:22.940
they came back with the news that

00:13:22.940 --> 00:13:25.940
Banu Quraidah has indeed broken the treaty

00:13:25.940 --> 00:13:27.940
they are assisting these allies against us

00:13:27.940 --> 00:13:29.940
and they were not supposed to do this

00:13:29.940 --> 00:13:31.940
so the Prophet salallahu alayhi wasalam

00:13:31.940 --> 00:13:32.940
sent two armies

00:13:32.940 --> 00:13:34.940
Salamah ibn Aslam radiallahu anhu

00:13:34.940 --> 00:13:36.940
with two hundred men

00:13:36.940 --> 00:13:37.940
and Zaid ibn Haritha

00:13:37.940 --> 00:13:38.940
with three hundred men

00:13:38.940 --> 00:13:40.940
protecting Madina Munawwar

00:13:40.940 --> 00:13:42.940
not fighting Banu Quraidah at the time

00:13:42.940 --> 00:13:44.940
but protecting Madina

00:13:44.940 --> 00:13:45.940
why was this?

00:13:45.940 --> 00:13:47.940
because he knew these people would have

00:13:47.940 --> 00:13:49.940
wanted to perhaps attack Madina

00:13:49.940 --> 00:13:51.940
or they may give passage

00:13:51.940 --> 00:13:53.940
to the allied forces

00:13:53.940 --> 00:13:55.940
in order to enter Madina

00:13:55.940 --> 00:13:56.940
and then there will be a problem

00:13:56.940 --> 00:13:58.940
where there will be a trench in front of us

00:13:58.940 --> 00:13:59.940
and the enemy behind us

00:13:59.940 --> 00:14:01.940
so in order to prevent that

00:14:01.940 --> 00:14:02.940
the Prophet salallahu alayhi wasalam

00:14:02.940 --> 00:14:04.940
sent these men

00:14:04.940 --> 00:14:05.940
and later on

00:14:05.940 --> 00:14:06.940
he also had sent

00:14:06.940 --> 00:14:09.940
Nu'ain ibn Mas'ud al-Ghatafani

00:14:09.940 --> 00:14:10.940
as we mentioned yesterday

00:14:10.940 --> 00:14:12.940
the one who went right to the enemy

00:14:12.940 --> 00:14:14.940
who did not know that he had accepted Islam

00:14:14.940 --> 00:14:15.940
Nu'ain ibn Mas'ud

00:14:15.940 --> 00:14:17.940
and he spoke to Ghatafan

00:14:17.940 --> 00:14:19.940
and told them that Quraysh is about to leave

00:14:19.940 --> 00:14:20.940
and they are not trusting you

00:14:20.940 --> 00:14:21.940
and he spoke to Quraysh

00:14:21.940 --> 00:14:23.940
and told them Ghatafan is not trusting you

00:14:23.940 --> 00:14:25.940
and he spoke to the Jewish tribe of Banu al-Nadir

00:14:25.940 --> 00:14:26.940
that had come

00:14:26.940 --> 00:14:27.940
the remnants of them

00:14:27.940 --> 00:14:29.940
who had come from Khaybar

00:14:29.940 --> 00:14:31.940
the likes of Huyay ibn Akhtab and so on

00:14:31.940 --> 00:14:33.940
and he told them do you know what?

00:14:33.940 --> 00:14:35.940
these people are full of mistrust

00:14:35.940 --> 00:14:36.940
and so on

00:14:36.940 --> 00:14:38.940
he had caused a lot of chaos on that day

00:14:38.940 --> 00:14:41.940
he also went to Banu Quraidah

00:14:41.940 --> 00:14:42.940
and he told them I'm warning you

00:14:42.940 --> 00:14:43.940
of what happened

00:14:43.940 --> 00:14:45.940
with Banu Qainuqa and Banu al-Nadir

00:14:45.940 --> 00:14:46.940
just be careful, be careful

00:14:46.940 --> 00:14:47.940
these people here

00:14:47.940 --> 00:14:49.940
they have some form of assistance with them

00:14:49.940 --> 00:14:50.940
which means the Muslims

00:14:50.940 --> 00:14:52.940
and so they were also frightened

00:14:52.940 --> 00:14:53.940
Banu Quraidah

00:14:53.940 --> 00:14:55.940
and Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:14:55.940 --> 00:14:57.940
protected the believers from

00:14:57.940 --> 00:15:01.940
the enemy of within Banu Quraidah

00:15:01.940 --> 00:15:02.940
and Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:15:02.940 --> 00:15:05.940
granted them victory over these allies

00:15:05.940 --> 00:15:07.940
who slowly but surely disappeared

00:15:07.940 --> 00:15:09.940
as we said the wind was so strong

00:15:09.940 --> 00:15:10.940
it was so cold

00:15:10.940 --> 00:15:12.940
it had extinguished their fire

00:15:12.940 --> 00:15:14.940
it had caused chaos in their tents

00:15:14.940 --> 00:15:18.940
it had also caused lots of difficulty

00:15:18.940 --> 00:15:19.940
in terms of health

00:15:19.940 --> 00:15:22.940
they were very cold, very ill, very sick

00:15:22.940 --> 00:15:23.940
they began to become

00:15:23.940 --> 00:15:24.940
and at the same time

00:15:24.940 --> 00:15:27.940
their horses were running amok

00:15:27.940 --> 00:15:28.940
because they were not used

00:15:28.940 --> 00:15:30.940
to this type of weather

00:15:30.940 --> 00:15:32.940
so they began to leave one after the other

00:15:32.940 --> 00:15:35.940
and Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala says

00:15:35.940 --> 00:15:37.940
remember we are the ones

00:15:37.940 --> 00:15:39.940
who chased them away

00:15:39.940 --> 00:15:41.940
we are the ones who granted you victory

00:15:41.940 --> 00:15:43.940
O messenger salallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:15:43.940 --> 00:15:44.940
Allah says

00:16:08.940 --> 00:16:10.940
remember when they had come from above

00:16:10.940 --> 00:16:12.940
they had come from above you

00:16:12.940 --> 00:16:13.940
and from beneath you

00:16:13.940 --> 00:16:15.940
ghatafan had come, quraysh had come

00:16:15.940 --> 00:16:17.940
Banu Quraidah had intended to harm

00:16:17.940 --> 00:16:20.940
and the people from khaybar had also come

00:16:20.940 --> 00:16:24.940
Allah says they came from all over

00:16:24.940 --> 00:16:27.940
and when the eyesight became dull

00:16:27.940 --> 00:16:28.940
meaning seeing so many people

00:16:28.940 --> 00:16:32.940
and the hearts had got right up to the throats

00:16:32.940 --> 00:16:34.940
imagine today when you are really really worried

00:16:34.940 --> 00:16:36.940
something major is happening

00:16:36.940 --> 00:16:38.940
where do you feel your pulse?

00:16:38.940 --> 00:16:39.940
you suddenly feel it

00:16:39.940 --> 00:16:41.940
as though your heart has gone right up to your neck

00:16:41.940 --> 00:16:42.940
and you can feel it there

00:16:42.940 --> 00:16:44.940
as though it wants to come out

00:16:44.940 --> 00:16:46.940
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala safeguard us

00:16:46.940 --> 00:16:48.940
Allah says at that point

00:16:48.940 --> 00:16:50.940
the Muslims were zulzilu

00:16:50.940 --> 00:16:53.940
they were tested, they were shaken

00:16:53.940 --> 00:16:56.940
a very severe shaking, awakening

00:16:56.940 --> 00:16:58.940
and their iman was tested

00:16:58.940 --> 00:17:01.940
and Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala says

00:17:01.940 --> 00:17:03.940
then they were granted victory

00:17:03.940 --> 00:17:04.940
Allahu Akbar

00:17:04.940 --> 00:17:06.940
after that they were granted victory

00:17:06.940 --> 00:17:08.940
when they had made dua to Allah

00:17:08.940 --> 00:17:11.940
and when they had laid their trust in Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:17:11.940 --> 00:17:13.940
so when the Prophet salallahu alayhi wasalam

00:17:13.940 --> 00:17:16.940
was now returning after the armies had left

00:17:16.940 --> 00:17:17.940
and he was coming back

00:17:17.940 --> 00:17:19.940
he was removing his armor

00:17:19.940 --> 00:17:22.940
and Jibreel alayhi salatu wasalam comes to him

00:17:22.940 --> 00:17:27.940
and says the angels have not yet declared this war over

00:17:27.940 --> 00:17:29.940
why was that?

00:17:29.940 --> 00:17:32.940
immediately the Prophet salallahu alayhi wasalam understood

00:17:32.940 --> 00:17:34.940
Banu Quraidah need to be fought

00:17:34.940 --> 00:17:36.940
because they broke their treaty

00:17:36.940 --> 00:17:38.940
they intended to kill us

00:17:38.940 --> 00:17:40.940
they sided with the other side

00:17:40.940 --> 00:17:42.940
and yet we had a treaty with them

00:17:42.940 --> 00:17:44.940
that we would be together on one side

00:17:44.940 --> 00:17:46.940
not aid the enemy against one another

00:17:46.940 --> 00:17:48.940
and because they did that

00:17:48.940 --> 00:17:49.940
the Prophet salallahu alayhi wasalam

00:17:49.940 --> 00:17:51.940
made a famous announcement

00:17:51.940 --> 00:17:52.940
he got up in his companions

00:17:52.940 --> 00:17:53.940
he says

00:18:02.940 --> 00:18:03.940
it was the time of Asr

00:18:03.940 --> 00:18:04.940
but he had said

00:18:04.940 --> 00:18:06.940
none of you should read Salatul Asr

00:18:06.940 --> 00:18:08.940
until you get to Banu Quraidah

00:18:08.940 --> 00:18:10.940
they immediately understood

00:18:10.940 --> 00:18:12.940
something is to happen

00:18:12.940 --> 00:18:13.940
they jumped on horseback

00:18:13.940 --> 00:18:14.940
and some of them began to even

00:18:14.940 --> 00:18:16.940
just run to Banu Quraidah

00:18:16.940 --> 00:18:17.940
with their weapons

00:18:17.940 --> 00:18:19.940
and on the way

00:18:19.940 --> 00:18:23.940
the time of Asr began to expire

00:18:23.940 --> 00:18:25.940
and I'm going to pause for a moment

00:18:25.940 --> 00:18:27.940
because we learn a lesson from this

00:18:27.940 --> 00:18:29.940
when the time of Asr began to expire

00:18:29.940 --> 00:18:33.940
the companions were divided into two groups

00:18:33.940 --> 00:18:34.940
one of them said

00:18:34.940 --> 00:18:36.940
let's read our Asr

00:18:36.940 --> 00:18:37.940
the other said

00:18:37.940 --> 00:18:39.940
didn't you hear the words of the Prophet?

00:18:39.940 --> 00:18:41.940
none of you should read Salatul Asr

00:18:41.940 --> 00:18:43.940
until you get to Banu Quraidah

00:18:43.940 --> 00:18:44.940
so we will adopt the words

00:18:44.940 --> 00:18:46.940
of the messenger salallahu alayhi wasalam

00:18:46.940 --> 00:18:48.940
we're going to get to Banu Quraidah

00:18:48.940 --> 00:18:49.940
then we will read our Asr there

00:18:49.940 --> 00:18:50.940
because today

00:18:50.940 --> 00:18:52.940
the time of Asr is not connected

00:18:52.940 --> 00:18:54.940
to the sun setting

00:18:54.940 --> 00:18:55.940
it's connected to the place

00:18:55.940 --> 00:18:57.940
it will not be valid for us to read it here

00:18:57.940 --> 00:18:58.940
when we've heard a statement

00:18:58.940 --> 00:18:59.940
do not read Asr

00:18:59.940 --> 00:19:01.940
until you get to Banu Quraidah

00:19:01.940 --> 00:19:02.940
you see what they were saying?

00:19:02.940 --> 00:19:03.940
and the other group said

00:19:03.940 --> 00:19:06.940
no, the messenger was only trying to say

00:19:06.940 --> 00:19:07.940
that rush to Banu Quraidah

00:19:07.940 --> 00:19:09.940
but he wasn't trying to say

00:19:09.940 --> 00:19:12.940
that delay your Asr until it's time expires

00:19:12.940 --> 00:19:13.940
so these were two

00:19:13.940 --> 00:19:15.940
totally different understandings

00:19:15.940 --> 00:19:17.940
one saying read your Salat

00:19:17.940 --> 00:19:18.940
the other one saying no

00:19:18.940 --> 00:19:19.940
let it become Qadha

00:19:19.940 --> 00:19:20.940
we read it later on

00:19:20.940 --> 00:19:21.940
and so what happened?

00:19:21.940 --> 00:19:24.940
they agreed that some of them would read

00:19:24.940 --> 00:19:25.940
whoever felt it was correct

00:19:25.940 --> 00:19:27.940
and they agreed that the others

00:19:27.940 --> 00:19:28.940
would read later on

00:19:28.940 --> 00:19:30.940
when the other party got to Banu Quraidah

00:19:30.940 --> 00:19:31.940
the time of Asr was over

00:19:31.940 --> 00:19:32.940
they read their Asr

00:19:32.940 --> 00:19:35.940
by that time this party had arrived

00:19:35.940 --> 00:19:37.940
so in actual fact

00:19:37.940 --> 00:19:38.940
they had not really lost time

00:19:38.940 --> 00:19:40.940
because these read Asr

00:19:40.940 --> 00:19:42.940
whilst the time displacement

00:19:42.940 --> 00:19:45.940
was the time it took to read Asr

00:19:45.940 --> 00:19:46.940
so when those got there

00:19:46.940 --> 00:19:48.940
they had got in time

00:19:48.940 --> 00:19:49.940
to read Salatul Asr

00:19:49.940 --> 00:19:52.940
enough time for these people to have arrived

00:19:52.940 --> 00:19:55.940
because they were both reading Salatul Asr

00:19:55.940 --> 00:19:56.940
when they met the messenger

00:19:56.940 --> 00:19:57.940
salallahu alaihi wasallam

00:19:57.940 --> 00:19:58.940
they told him

00:19:58.940 --> 00:19:59.940
what had happened?

00:19:59.940 --> 00:20:02.940
and very amazing

00:20:02.940 --> 00:20:03.940
very amazing words

00:20:03.940 --> 00:20:04.940
of the Prophet salallahu alaihi wasallam

00:20:04.940 --> 00:20:06.940
he says both of you are correct

00:20:06.940 --> 00:20:07.940
why was that?

00:20:07.940 --> 00:20:10.940
what was the intention of either party

00:20:10.940 --> 00:20:11.940
to follow his words?

00:20:11.940 --> 00:20:13.940
these people did what they did

00:20:13.940 --> 00:20:14.940
following his words

00:20:14.940 --> 00:20:15.940
but their interpretation

00:20:15.940 --> 00:20:16.940
was slightly different

00:20:16.940 --> 00:20:18.940
and these people did what they did

00:20:18.940 --> 00:20:19.940
because they followed his words

00:20:19.940 --> 00:20:21.940
their interpretation was slightly different

00:20:21.940 --> 00:20:22.940
he says

00:20:22.940 --> 00:20:25.940
for as long as you intended obedience

00:20:25.940 --> 00:20:26.940
you are correct

00:20:26.940 --> 00:20:27.940
Subhanallah

00:20:27.940 --> 00:20:28.940
look at this

00:20:28.940 --> 00:20:29.940
and this is why we learn

00:20:29.940 --> 00:20:31.940
that sometimes within the Sharia

00:20:31.940 --> 00:20:33.940
there may be more than one way of doing things

00:20:33.940 --> 00:20:35.940
and both of those ways may be correct

00:20:35.940 --> 00:20:37.940
there is no point for us

00:20:37.940 --> 00:20:39.940
to shove down the throats of people

00:20:39.940 --> 00:20:41.940
something that we believe is correct

00:20:41.940 --> 00:20:43.940
when there is evidence to prove

00:20:43.940 --> 00:20:45.940
that they also are

00:20:45.940 --> 00:20:47.940
upon the understanding of what the messenger

00:20:47.940 --> 00:20:49.940
salallahu alaihi wasallam has said

00:20:49.940 --> 00:20:50.940
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:20:50.940 --> 00:20:52.940
grant us a deep understanding

00:20:52.940 --> 00:20:54.940
this happened at the time of the battle

00:20:54.940 --> 00:20:56.940
just after the battle of Ahzab

00:20:56.940 --> 00:20:58.940
on their way to Banu Qurayza

00:20:58.940 --> 00:20:59.940
remember this

00:20:59.940 --> 00:21:02.940
it's a very very beautiful incident that occurred

00:21:02.940 --> 00:21:04.940
now when they got to Banu Qurayza

00:21:04.940 --> 00:21:05.940
the prophet salallahu alaihi wasallam

00:21:05.940 --> 00:21:07.940
surrounded them for 25 nights

00:21:07.940 --> 00:21:11.940
and they started asking questions at that time

00:21:11.940 --> 00:21:14.940
because they thought that we are going to be protected

00:21:14.940 --> 00:21:15.940
by our force

00:21:15.940 --> 00:21:17.940
and after some time they became frightened

00:21:17.940 --> 00:21:20.940
because they had lasted longer than

00:21:20.940 --> 00:21:22.940
Banu Al-Nadheer and Banu Qaynuqa

00:21:22.940 --> 00:21:25.940
and they were perhaps the worst of the lot

00:21:26.940 --> 00:21:28.940
and so they started talking

00:21:28.940 --> 00:21:32.940
okay please send us away like Banu Qaynuqa was sent away

00:21:32.940 --> 00:21:33.940
the messenger says no

00:21:33.940 --> 00:21:36.940
well then do what you did to Banu Al-Nadheer with us

00:21:36.940 --> 00:21:37.940
he says no

00:21:37.940 --> 00:21:40.940
so then they began talking

00:21:40.940 --> 00:21:42.940
what should happen because you wanted to fight

00:21:42.940 --> 00:21:43.940
you are criminals

00:21:43.940 --> 00:21:45.940
you are the people who are

00:21:45.940 --> 00:21:48.940
really guilty of war crimes against humanity

00:21:48.940 --> 00:21:50.940
and this is what you have done

00:21:50.940 --> 00:21:53.940
it is easy to know what they had done

00:21:53.940 --> 00:21:55.940
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala protect us

00:21:55.940 --> 00:21:57.940
had it not been for the protection of Allah

00:21:57.940 --> 00:22:00.940
subhanahu wa ta'ala one wonders what might have happened

00:22:00.940 --> 00:22:02.940
to the people in Madina Munawwara

00:22:02.940 --> 00:22:04.940
and so the prophet salallahu alaihi wasallam then

00:22:04.940 --> 00:22:06.940
agreed to what they had to say

00:22:06.940 --> 00:22:07.940
they said okay

00:22:07.940 --> 00:22:11.940
we have a person who was alive to us in the past

00:22:11.940 --> 00:22:13.940
and his name is Sa'd ibn Mu'adh

00:22:13.940 --> 00:22:15.940
the head of Al-Aws

00:22:15.940 --> 00:22:18.940
in fact before they got to the head of Al-Aws

00:22:18.940 --> 00:22:21.940
the prophet salallahu alaihi wasallam sent Abu Lubaba

00:22:22.940 --> 00:22:23.940
remember this name

00:22:23.940 --> 00:22:25.940
Abu Lubaba ibn Abdul Munzir

00:22:25.940 --> 00:22:27.940
r.a.w. was sent

00:22:27.940 --> 00:22:31.940
because he had a link with the people of Banu Qurayza

00:22:31.940 --> 00:22:33.940
and he even had some family there

00:22:33.940 --> 00:22:35.940
because of that the prophet salallahu alaihi wasallam

00:22:35.940 --> 00:22:37.940
sends him and told him

00:22:37.940 --> 00:22:39.940
go and speak to them and tell them

00:22:39.940 --> 00:22:41.940
what we are saying and so on

00:22:41.940 --> 00:22:43.940
when he went there they asked him

00:22:43.940 --> 00:22:47.940
should we settle for what the messenger is saying

00:22:47.940 --> 00:22:49.940
and he told them yes

00:22:49.940 --> 00:22:51.940
and he pointed at his neck

00:22:51.940 --> 00:22:52.940
yes

00:22:52.940 --> 00:22:55.940
which means you people are going to be executed

00:22:55.940 --> 00:22:57.940
you are all criminals

00:22:57.940 --> 00:22:58.940
yes

00:22:58.940 --> 00:22:59.940
they were shocked

00:22:59.940 --> 00:23:00.940
but they understood

00:23:00.940 --> 00:23:02.940
when he did that

00:23:02.940 --> 00:23:05.940
he was not instructed by the messenger salallahu alaihi wasallam

00:23:05.940 --> 00:23:06.940
to tell them that

00:23:06.940 --> 00:23:07.940
not at all

00:23:07.940 --> 00:23:09.940
so he felt immediately

00:23:09.940 --> 00:23:12.940
that I have engaged in some form of deception

00:23:12.940 --> 00:23:15.940
I did something I was not supposed to do

00:23:15.940 --> 00:23:16.940
and I have sinned

00:23:16.940 --> 00:23:18.940
because I went and gave away

00:23:18.940 --> 00:23:20.940
something that I knew of the messenger

00:23:20.940 --> 00:23:22.940
which I was not instructed to give away

00:23:22.940 --> 00:23:24.940
he came back without going to

00:23:24.940 --> 00:23:25.940
Rasulullah salallahu alaihi wasallam

00:23:25.940 --> 00:23:26.940
he was very shy

00:23:26.940 --> 00:23:28.940
he ran to al-madinah al-munawwara

00:23:28.940 --> 00:23:30.940
he went to masjid of Rasulullah salallahu alaihi wasallam

00:23:30.940 --> 00:23:32.940
and he tied himself

00:23:32.940 --> 00:23:34.940
on one of the pillars

00:23:34.940 --> 00:23:35.940
it was a tree stump

00:23:35.940 --> 00:23:36.940
he tied himself

